      <title>两名参议员批评美联储监管机构内部交易报告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/two-senators-criticize-fed-watchdog-over-internal-trading-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名美国参议员批评美联储内部监管机构在疫情期间对美联储官员的交易进行调查，称其未能追究机构官员的责任，也未能采取措施防止未来发生类似丑闻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/two-senators-criticize-fed-watchdog-over-internal-trading-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亨特削减个人税，保守党寻求选举年提振</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/hunt-says-uk-growth-better-than-expected-in-boost-for-tories</link>
      <description><![CDATA[杰里米·亨特 (Jeremy Hunt) 宣布将国家保险工资税再次削减 2 个百分点，这是向选民赠送的礼物，因为执政的保守党试图在预计今年晚些时候举行的大选之前重新赢得公众支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/hunt-says-uk-growth-better-than-expected-in-boost-for-tories</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 12:56:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
